Title: Naka-Choko
Plot: The bond between Hannibal and Will grows after Will demonstrates his willingness to go to dark places, a shift that does not go unnoticed by Jack. Jack and the FBI team investigate a tableau made of Randal Tier and his animal exoskeleton, fully realized as the vicious hunter he yearned to be.
ParentalRatingReason: R18 Violence,sex scenes and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Michael Pitt, Katharine Isabelle, Lara Jean Chorostecki, Mark O'Brien
